Class Vector2

  • java.lang.Object
    • thothbot.parallax.core.shared.core.Vector2
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Vector
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Vector3

    public class Vector2
extends java.lang.Object
implements Vector
    This class is realization of (X, Y) vector. Where: X - x coordinate of the vector. Y - y coordinate of the vector.
    Author:
    thothbot
